{"id":68,"parent_id":48,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":68,"title":"Luke 20","subtitle":"","short_title":"Luke","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 20"],[".studySummary",["i","The chief priests oppose Jesus—He gives the parable of the wicked husbandmen—Render unto Cæsar and God that which is theirs—Jesus teaches the law of marriage."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.1","order":"03.05.020.8246"},["b","1"],"And it came to pass,",["i","that"],"on one of those days, as he taught the people in the temple, and preached the gospel, the chief priests and the scribes came upon",["i","him"],"with the elders,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.2","order":"03.05.020.8247"},["b","2"],"And spake unto him, saying, Tell us, by what authority doest thou these things? or who is he that gave thee this authority?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.3","order":"03.05.020.8248"},["b","3"],"And he answered and said unto them, I will also ask you one thing; and answer me:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.4","order":"03.05.020.8249"},["b","4"],"The baptism of John, was it from heaven, or of men?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.5","order":"03.05.020.8250"},["b","5"],"And they reasoned with themselves, saying, If we shall say, From heaven; he will say, Why then believed ye him not?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.6","order":"03.05.020.8251"},["b","6"],"But and if we say, Of men; all the people will stone us: for they be persuaded that John was a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"prophet"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.7","order":"03.05.020.8252"},["b","7"],"And they answered, that they could not tell whence",["i","it was."]],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.8","order":"03.05.020.8253"},["b","8"],"And Jesus said unto them, Neither tell I you by what authority I do these things."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.9","order":"03.05.020.8254"},["b","9"],"Then began he to speak to the people this parable; A certain man planted a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"vineyard"],", and let it forth to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"husbandmen"],", and went into a far country for a long time."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.10","order":"03.05.020.8255"},["b","10"],"And at the season he sent a servant to the husbandmen, that they should give him of the fruit of the vineyard: but the husbandmen beat him, and sent",["i","him"],"away empty."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.11","order":"03.05.020.8256"},["b","11"],"And again he sent another servant: and they beat him also, and entreated",["i","him"],"shamefully, and sent",["i","him"],"away empty."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.12","order":"03.05.020.8257"},["b","12"],"And again he sent a third: and they wounded him also, and cast",["i","him"],"out."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.13","order":"03.05.020.8258"},["b","13"],"Then said the lord of the vineyard, What shall I do? I will send my beloved son: it may be they will reverence",["i","him"],"when they see him."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.14","order":"03.05.020.8259"},["b","14"],"But when the husbandmen saw him, they reasoned among themselves, saying, This is the heir: come, let us kill him, that the inheritance may be ours."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.15","order":"03.05.020.8260"},["b","15"],"So they cast him out of the vineyard, and killed",["i","him."],"What therefore shall the lord of the vineyard do unto them?"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.16","order":"03.05.020.8261"},["b","16"],"He shall come and destroy these husbandmen, and shall give the vineyard to others. And when they heard",["i","it,"],"they said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"God forbid"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.17","order":"03.05.020.8262"},["b","17"],"And he beheld them, and said, What is this then that is written, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"stone"],"which the builders rejected, the same is become the head of the corner?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.18","order":"03.05.020.8263"},["b","18"],"Whosoever shall fall upon that stone shall be broken; but on whomsoever it shall fall, it will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"grind him to powder"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.19","order":"03.05.020.8264"},["b","19"],"¶And the chief priests and the scribes the same hour sought to lay hands on him; and they feared the people: for they perceived that he had spoken this parable against them."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.20","order":"03.05.020.8265"},["b","20"],"And they watched",["i","him,"],"and sent forth spies, which should feign themselves just men, that they might",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"take"],"hold of his words, that so they might deliver him unto the power and authority of the governor."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.21","order":"03.05.020.8266"},["b","21"],"And they asked him, saying, Master, we know that thou sayest and teachest rightly, neither acceptest thou the person",["i","of any,"],"but teachest the way of God truly:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.22","order":"03.05.020.8267"},["b","22"],"Is it lawful for us to give",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"tribute"],"unto Cæsar, or no?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.23","order":"03.05.020.8268"},["b","23"],"But he perceived their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"craftiness"],", and said unto them, Why tempt ye me?"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.24","order":"03.05.020.8269"},["b","24"],"Shew me a penny. Whose image and superscription hath it? They answered and said, Cæsar’s."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.25","order":"03.05.020.8270"},["b","25"],"And he said unto them, Render therefore unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Cæsar"],"the things which be Cæsar’s, and unto God the things which be God’s."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.26","order":"03.05.020.8271"},["b","26"],"And they could not take hold of his words before the people: and they marvelled at his answer, and held their peace."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.27","order":"03.05.020.8272"},["b","27"],"¶Then came to",["i","him"],"certain of the Sadducees, which deny that there is any resurrection; and they asked him,"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.28","order":"03.05.020.8273"},["b","28"],"Saying, Master, Moses wrote unto us, If any man’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"brother"],"die, having a wife, and he die without children, that his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"brother"],"should take his wife, and raise up seed unto his brother."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.29","order":"03.05.020.8274"},["b","29"],"There were therefore seven brethren: and the first took a wife, and died without children."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.30","order":"03.05.020.8275"},["b","30"],"And the second took her to wife, and he died childless."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.31","order":"03.05.020.8276"},["b","31"],"And the third took her; and in like manner the seven also: and they left no children, and died."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.32","order":"03.05.020.8277"},["b","32"],"Last of all the woman died also."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.33","order":"03.05.020.8278"},["b","33"],"Therefore in the resurrection whose wife of them is she? for seven had her to wife."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.34","order":"03.05.020.8279"},["b","34"],"And Jesus answering said unto them, The children of this world",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"marry"],", and are given in marriage:"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.35","order":"03.05.020.8280"},["b","35"],"But they which shall be accounted worthy to obtain",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"that"],"world, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_35b"},"resurrection"],"from the dead, neither marry, nor are given in",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_35c"},"marriage"],":"],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.36","order":"03.05.020.8281"},["b","36"],"Neither can they die any more: for they are equal unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"angels"],"; and are the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"children"],"of God, being the children of the resurrection."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.37","order":"03.05.020.8282"},["b","37"],"Now that the dead are raised, even Moses shewed at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"bush"],", when he calleth the Lord the God of Abraham, and the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.38","order":"03.05.020.8283"},["b","38"],"For he is not a God of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"dead"],", but of the living: for all live unto him."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.39","order":"03.05.020.8284"},["b","39"],"¶Then certain of the scribes answering said, Master, thou hast well said."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.40","order":"03.05.020.8285"},["b","40"],"And after that they durst not ask him any",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"question"],"at all."]],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.41","order":"03.05.020.8286"},["b","41"],"And he said unto them, How say they that Christ is David’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"son"],"?"],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.42","order":"03.05.020.8287"},["b","42"],"And David himself saith in the book of Psalms, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"Lord"],", Sit thou on my right hand,"],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.43","order":"03.05.020.8288"},["b","43"],"Till I make thine enemies thy footstool."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.44","order":"03.05.020.8289"},["b","44"],"David therefore calleth him Lord, how is he then his son?"],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.45","order":"03.05.020.8290"},["b","45"],"¶Then in the audience of all the people he said unto his disciples,"],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.46","order":"03.05.020.8291"},["b","46"],"Beware of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_46a"},"scribes"],", which desire to walk in long robes, and love greetings in the markets, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_46b"},"highest"],"seats in the synagogues, and the chief rooms at feasts;"],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.47","order":"03.05.020.8292"},["b","47"],"Which devour widows’ houses, and for a shew make long prayers: the same shall receive greater damnation."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.6a","order":"03.05.020.8293"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.9"},"Matt. 11:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/14.5"},"14:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/21.26"},"21:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.9a","order":"03.05.020.8295"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vineyard-of-the-lord"},"TG Vineyard of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.9b","order":"03.05.020.8297"},["b","9b"],["span.small","GR"],"farmers."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.16a","order":"03.05.020.8299"},["b","16a"],["span.small","GR"],"May it not be."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.17a","order":"03.05.020.8301"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rock"},"TG Rock"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.18a","order":"03.05.020.8303"},["b","18a"],["span.small","GR"],"scatter like chaff."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.20a","order":"03.05.020.8305"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.15.15-22"},"Matt. 22:15 (15–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.13.13-17"},"Mark 12:13 (13–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.22a","order":"03.05.020.8307"},["b","22a"],["span.small","GR"],"taxes.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.21.21-22"},"D&C 58:21 (21–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.9.4-10"},"98:9 (4–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.23a","order":"03.05.020.8309"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/10.17"},"Alma 10:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/10.25.21-27"},"D&C 10:25 (21–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.25a","order":"03.05.020.8311"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.22.21-23"},"D&C 58:22 (21–23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.26.25-29"},"63:26 (25–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.28a","order":"03.05.020.8313"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/25.5"},"Deut. 25:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.28b","order":"03.05.020.8315"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.19"},"Mark 12:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.34a","order":"03.05.020.8317"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-marry"},"TG Marriage, Marry"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-temporal"},"Marriage, Temporal"],"."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.35a","order":"03.05.020.8319"},["b","35a"],["span.small","JST"],"Luke 20:35 … that world,",["i","through"],"resurrection from …"],["div",{"id":"35b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.35b","order":"03.05.020.8321"},["b","35b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/objectives"},"TG Objectives"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"35c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.35c","order":"03.05.020.8323"},["b","35c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.16.7-39"},"D&C 132:16 (7–39)"],"."],["div",{"id":"36a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.36a","order":"03.05.020.8325"},["b","36a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/131.2.1-4"},"D&C 131:2 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.17.5-17"},"132:17 (5–17)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"36b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.36b","order":"03.05.020.8327"},["b","36b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"},"TG Sons and Daughters of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"37a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.37a","order":"03.05.020.8329"},["b","37a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.2.2-6"},"Ex. 3:2 (2–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.38a","order":"03.05.020.8331"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/14.9"},"Rom. 14:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-disembodied"},"TG Spirits, Disembodied"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.40a","order":"03.05.020.8333"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.116"},"D&C 84:116"],"."],["div",{"id":"41a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.41a","order":"03.05.020.8335"},["b","41a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/1.16.1-16"},"Matt. 1:16 (1–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.14.3-17"},"D&C 93:14 (3–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"42a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.42a","order":"03.05.020.8337"},["b","42a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/110.1"},"Ps. 110:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"46a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.46a","order":"03.05.020.8339"},["b","46a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.16"},"2 Ne. 28:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/10.27"},"Alma 10:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"46b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.46b","order":"03.05.020.8341"},["b","46b"],["span.small","GR"],"first or most honorable.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/11.43"},"Luke 11:43"],"."]]}
